ces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點計息？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0bd9d8764d71041ca77208bc1d0618e3f92fa92","tid":1028889,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T22:36:12.000Z","msg":"定期1.56厘? <br />\n真係唔做research就可以出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c2c219089a10f2ec9367f0b8c1e60dc0f072e2","tid":1028889,"uid":148390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0bd9d8764d71041ca77208bc1d0618e3f92fa92","tid":1028889,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T22:36:12.000Z","msg":"定期1.56厘? <br />\n真係唔做research就可以出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T22:42:50.000Z","msg":"唔計特別優惠，好似真係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然識玩一定係做唔同銀行嘅特別優惠定期"},{"pid":"0db66c7e1ac864f204f37c653c3c40329959a835","tid":1028889,"uid":144843,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T23:29:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0737699f24a7fc6fc42897d341e347dea9d31211","tid":1028889,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T23:42:50.000Z","msg":"開佢個基金戶口會唔會令原本個現金戶口變左孖展戶口架。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090cde15bc92692bafad39c884a6f199fde262ae","tid":1028889,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T23:44:08.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}